data.description: Located just 15 minutes from both Ft Sam and Randolph AFB, this beautiful 3 bed/2 bath home, boast over 2500 sq ft of single story living space.  Walk up to a lightly landscaped house and enter to see large living area or elegant dining area.  The kitchen features tons of storage, granite countertops, black finished appliances.  The back yard boasts a huge covered and screened in patio with doggy door, ready for entertainment or a nice quiet place for reading and/or coffee.  Oversize extended garage to accommodate vehicles and work station.  Shop lights have been installed for pinpoint lighting.  45 solar panels will convey with purchase and transferred to new owner, soft water hookups available, and leaf guard gutter system installed.
